<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">خشيه يخشاه خشية:</span> خافه واتقاه.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">خشي:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(ذَلِكَ لِمَنْ خَشِيَ الْعَنَتَ مِنْكُمْ)</span> <span style="color:#950000">" ٢٥/النساء"</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">تخشي:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(فَاضْرِبْ لَهُمْ طَرِيقاً فِي الْبَحْرِ يَبَساً لا تَخَافُ دَرَكاً وَلا تَخْشَى)</span> <span style="color:#950000">" ٧٧/طه"</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أي ولا تخشي ما يمنعك من الووصل سالما.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">واخشون:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(الْيَوْمَ يَئِسَ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا مِنْ دِينِكُمْ فَلا تَخْشَوْهُمْ وَاخْشَوْنِي)</span> <span style="color:#950000">" ٣/المائدة "</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>حذفت ياء المتكلم تخفيفا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[خ ص ص]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٤ كلمات<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#008000">(يختص - خاصة - خصاصة)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١ -<span style="color:#006d98"> خص فلانا بالشئ يخصه خصا:</span> أفرده به دون غيره. ومثله اختصه به اختصاصا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">يختص:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(وَاللَّهُ يَخْتَصُّ بِرَحْمَتِهِ مَنْ يَشَاءُ)</span> <span style="color:#950000">"١٠٥/البقرة "</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وخاصة:</span> ضد عامة.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>